  TEAHUPO'O, Tahiti (AP) - As the heavy, barrel-shaped waves of Teahupo'o, Tahiti - where the Paris Olympics surfing competition is being held - crashed in the distance, another, smaller surf session was underway just off the shore.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Winnipeg Free Press\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999989469580302, \"rank\": 1.0520962834095487e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read this article for free:    Already have an account?Log in here \\u00bb  To continue reading, please subscribe:  $0 for the first 4 weeks*  *No charge for 4 weeks then price increases to the regular rate of $19.00 plus GST every four weeks.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Offer available to new and qualified returning subscribers only.\", \"f