\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read unlimited articles for free today:    Already have an account?Log in here \\u00bb  Hey there, time traveller!This article was published01/08/2024(488 days ago), so information in it may no longer be current.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TEAHUPO'O, Tahiti (AP) - As the heavy, barrel-shaped waves of Teahupo'o, Tahiti - where the Paris Olympics surfing competition is being held - crashed in the distance, another, smaller surf session was underway just off the shore.\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 2553, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999989469580302, \"rank\": 1.0520962834095487e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 2607, \"end\": 2613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Go, go, go!\\\"\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"one lanky teenager with sun-bleached hair yelled in French to another, sitting on their surfboards in the ocean.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Allez, allez!\\\"\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Seconds later, whoops and whistles of approval from other young surfers in the water and parents sitting on the beach filled the air, as 14-year-old French Polynesian surfer Kiara Goold cruised along a 4-foot-high (1.2-meter-high) wave, smiling.\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 3155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3059, \"end\": 3065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 3084, \"end\": 3089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kiara_Advani\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 1.856475953549488e-12, \"text\": \"Kiara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kiara_Advani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kiara_Advani\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a sight locals and visitors to Tahiti would not have been able to see until recently, 38-year-old French Polynesian professional surfer Michel Bourez said.\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3193, \"end\": 3199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 3260, \"end\": 3266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 3267, \"end\": 3277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9999994704754992, \"rank\": 4.721487649801767e-07, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 3298, \"end\": 3311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michel_Bourez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michel Bourez\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michel_Bourez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michel_Bourez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Back in the day, there were no kids surfing,\\\" said Bourez, who first hopped on a board as a teenager.\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Teahupo'o has been a coveted destination for surfers from around the world for decades, it's only in more recent years that local surf culture and talent among younger generations began to develop across Tahiti.\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3633, \"end\": 3639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With two French Polynesian surfers included in the 2024 Olympics, the surfing community expects local interest in the sport to grow.\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3650, \"end\": 3656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 3657, \"end\": 3667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9999994704754992, \"rank\": 4.721487649801767e-07, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Locals said Bourez has been a steward in the development of local surfing talent and culture in recent years.\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Partly driven by the lack of resources he had when starting out and then finding success in his own career, Bourez said he began training talented young local surfers he spotted across the island's shores.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 4090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Otherwise, all the knowledge that I gained during all these years will be gone - and for no reason,\\\" Bourez said.\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have to give back to the local community and surfers.\\\"\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Goold is one of the young local surfers Bourez has mentored.\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in French Polynesia, Goold said she has spent time on the ocean since before she could remember, but only got serious about surfing around age 8.\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I challenge myself by doing things that maybe I do not want to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That means hitting the gym and surfing when the waves are really big.\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just try to train really hard.\\\"\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Goold said she feels it's paid off: she's traveled internationally to compete and won youth tournaments at home in French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4793, \"end\": 4802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9984275903892936, \"rank\": 0.0015748859766186259, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But most days, she can be found with other young surfers along the shores of Tahiti, catching waves and playfully competing against each other.\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4882, \"end\": 4888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7711481973455582e-11, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We keep pushing each other,\\\" Goold said with a laugh.\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 5004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just hang out, and it's super fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 5005, \"to\": 5044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The inclusion of two French Polynesian surfers - Vahin\\u00e9 Fierro and Kauli Vaast - in the Paris Olympics also has been a major boost for the promotion and development of local surfing, Bourez said.\", \"from\": 5046, \"to\": 5241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5067, \"end\": 5073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 5074, \"end\": 5084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9999994704754992, \"rank\": 4.721487649801767e-07, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 5119, \"end\": 5124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have become kids' idols here,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 5243, \"to\": 5288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fierro and Vaast know they have inspired young local surfers.\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5301, \"end\": 5306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the best thing in the world, because I was them a couple years ago,\\\" Vaast said after winning his second round heat.\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5431, \"end\": 5436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We try to do our best, to give the best energy, the best personality for them.\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We try to be the best example possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vahine, who was the first Tahitian wild card to claim a victory during the World Surf League at Teahupo'o, said the shift in surfing culture for French Polynesian women has been especially noticeable.\", \"from\": 5601, \"to\": 5801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5627, \"end\": 5635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999997189661, \"rank\": 2.2100608565706498e-10, \"text\": \"Tahitian\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 5676, \"end\": 5693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.238276504840372e-24, \"text\": \"World Surf League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}, {\"begin\": 5746, \"end\": 5752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have really seen the change, whether it's out here at home, or on the beach breaks.\", \"from\": 5803, \"to\": 5889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is almost as many girls as men, and it's really cool to see,\\\" Fierro said.\", \"from\": 5890, \"to\": 5970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Goold plans to have years of surfing and competition ahead of her, she said she already knows what she will say to the next generation of French Polynesian surfers who might come asking her for advice.\", \"from\": 5972, \"to\": 6179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6116, \"end\": 6122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.688474668830119, \"rank\": 0.45205555936777003, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 6123, \"end\": 6133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.9999994704754992, \"rank\": 4.721487649801767e-07, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to say, 'Follow you dreams - the only thing you can do for now is work really hard and stay positive.\", \"from\": 6181, \"to\": 6294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Have fun.'\\\"\", \"from\": 6295, \"to\": 6306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___  AP Summer Olympics: https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games  AdvertisementAdvertise With Us  AdvertisementAdvertise With Us  Advertisement  Learn more about Winnipeg Free Press Advertising solutions\", \"from\": 6308, \"to\": 6519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6313, \"end\": 6315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999989469580302, \"rank\": 1.0520962834095487e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 6478, \"end\": 6497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Winnipeg Free Press\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\"}]}]}"